It was uncovered in May 1986 by Italian Police and <link>
Armando Carbone</link>, a friend of <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9638700866880419">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../439/6182439.xml">
Italo Allodi</link></person>
